  Chloe, 20, is a native New Yorker with a passion for travel, regularly sharing photographs of her trips abroad to social media. The actress has 98,700 Instagram followers and loves to share stunning snaps of herself looking chic and glamorous. Stephanie is a senior college student and looks almost unrecognisable from the bubblegum pink persona she once portrayed. Chloe became an overnight child star upon joining LazyTown in 2013 after it had a four year break, originally airing in 2004.   